WEBVTT

1
00:02:11.654 --> 00:02:14.714
Mrs. Li? You're so beautiful.

2
00:02:14.824 --> 00:02:17.520
They say your dumplings
are the most expensive.


3
00:02:17.627 --> 00:02:20.289
Of course! Please come in.

4
00:02:21.631 --> 00:02:23.599
You've come at the right time!

5
00:02:23.699 --> 00:02:26.930
The water is just boiling,
waiting for you.


6
00:02:33.609 --> 00:02:36.669
Actually, I know who you are.

7
00:02:36.779 --> 00:02:39.976
I watched you on TV very often
when I first came to Hong Kong.


8
00:02:40.082 --> 00:02:41.344
You were the best!

9
00:02:41.450 --> 00:02:43.509
I quit acting a long time ago.

10
00:02:48.257 --> 00:02:50.122
Please, have a seat.

11
00:02:50.226 --> 00:02:52.217
Mrs. Li, guess how old I am.

12
00:03:00.169 --> 00:03:01.158
I suppose...

13
00:03:02.271 --> 00:03:04.239
you're in your thirties at most.

14
00:03:06.209 --> 00:03:09.770
I'm much older than that.
Everyone calls me Aunt Mei.


15
00:03:14.050 --> 00:03:15.677
But you don't have any wrinkles.

16
00:03:15.785 --> 00:03:18.276
And I have fair skin, too.

17
00:03:18.387 --> 00:03:21.879
I'm my own best advertisement.

18
00:03:22.925 --> 00:03:25.951
Your skin is great. 
I'm impressed.

19
00:03:26.996 --> 00:03:33.902
My dumplings are worth it.
You get what you pay for.


20
00:04:25.388 --> 00:04:27.856
Mrs. Li...

21
00:04:28.491 --> 00:04:30.550
Want me to put in more cabbage?

22
00:04:31.160 --> 00:04:32.787
It's up to you.

23
00:04:32.895 --> 00:04:34.453
The Northerners always say,

24
00:04:34.563 --> 00:04:38.624
"Good feeling comes from a nap.
Good taste comes from a dumpling."


25
00:04:38.734 --> 00:04:41.703
Dumplings have existed in China
for more than 1400 years.


26
00:04:43.306 --> 00:04:45.604
But the Southerners still say

27
00:04:45.708 --> 00:04:50.111
they're just dough stuffed
with meat, nothing special!


28
00:04:58.220 --> 00:05:04.648
I use high-gluten flour
for texture and chewiness.


29
00:05:04.760 --> 00:05:11.359
I knead it fine until
it's like a peeled egg.


30
00:05:11.467 --> 00:05:15.460
Smooth, translucent and soft.

31
00:05:19.608 --> 00:05:23.476
That's the secret to keep
the filling from leaking out.


32
00:06:06.188 --> 00:06:13.026
So that the juicy flavor explodes
in the mouth, eat while it's warm.


33
00:06:13.129 --> 00:06:14.960
I eat these often.

34
00:06:15.064 --> 00:06:21.230
Sometimes in soup, sometimes minced
and steamed with citrus peel.


35
00:06:34.650 --> 00:06:38.984
Just think of the results,
not what it was.


36
00:06:56.639 --> 00:07:02.373
For women to rejuvenate, you must start
from inside for the best result.


37
00:07:05.581 --> 00:07:08.641
Only my secret formula can do this.

38
00:07:14.156 --> 00:07:15.953
Let me sing for you.

39
00:07:16.058 --> 00:07:18.993
Well, it's kind of a custom of mine.

40
00:07:19.095 --> 00:07:21.928
I often sing songs from my youth
when my customers eat.


41
00:07:22.031 --> 00:07:25.296
Take it as entertainment.
Listen.


42
00:07:28.537 --> 00:07:36.637
The water of Hung Lake is rough

43
00:07:36.745 --> 00:07:44.584
My home is on the shore

44
00:07:44.687 --> 00:07:52.719
At dawn, boats go out with nets

45
00:07:52.828 --> 00:08:02.828
At dusk, they return loaded with fish

46
00:08:04.473 --> 00:08:12.938
Wild ducks and lotus roots are here

47
00:08:13.048 --> 00:08:20.147
Autumns are bountiful with rice

48
00:08:20.256 --> 00:08:24.852
They say heaven is beautiful

49
00:08:24.960 --> 00:08:31.729
How can it compare with Hung Lake

50
00:09:23.485 --> 00:09:26.283
You were already on a trip last week.

51
00:09:26.388 --> 00:09:28.822
You promised to stay
for our 15th anniversary.


52
00:09:29.858 --> 00:09:33.089
I'm just going for a few days.
I'll try to come back early.


53
00:09:33.195 --> 00:09:38.098
It's boring here in the hotel.

54
00:09:38.200 --> 00:09:41.658
We'll move into our new home
as soon as the renovation is over.


55
00:09:49.111 --> 00:09:52.046
See if there's anything else
we need in the new house.


56
00:09:54.383 --> 00:09:56.647
So many zeroes?

57
00:09:58.454 --> 00:10:00.149
You used to laugh a lot.

58
00:10:01.190 --> 00:10:03.556
Now even a big fat check
can't make you happy?


59
00:10:03.659 --> 00:10:06.822
You're not taking me along.

60
00:10:06.929 --> 00:10:09.625
Why should I be happy?

61
00:10:09.732 --> 00:10:13.361
- I'll be gone for only four or five days.
- And if not?


62
00:10:15.771 --> 00:10:18.296
I'll write you another check as a fine.

63
00:10:19.341 --> 00:10:21.468
Fines are for mistakes.

64
00:10:22.278 --> 00:10:23.836
Whatever.

65
00:10:27.549 --> 00:10:31.417
About that contract... If you don't send it
over soon, I'm going to change my mind.


66
00:10:46.001 --> 00:10:49.164
I went through so much to get these.

67
00:10:49.271 --> 00:10:52.536
- They're stepping up the surveillance.
- Because some paparazzi have come.


68
00:10:52.641 --> 00:10:54.233
Hong Kong media is so nosy.

69
00:10:55.077 --> 00:10:57.341
Just don't show up
in the next two weeks.


70
00:10:57.446 --> 00:10:59.676
Even the locals can't get
hold of the stock now.


71
00:10:59.782 --> 00:11:01.306
We'll see.

72
00:11:01.417 --> 00:11:04.409
- Thanks.
- This is for you.


73
00:11:04.520 --> 00:11:08.422
This way, miss.
This way, miss.


74
00:11:13.962 --> 00:11:15.953
- Put it through
- Over there?


75
00:11:16.065 --> 00:11:18.363
- The lunchbox
- Okay.


76
00:11:41.357 --> 00:11:42.915
Mrs. Li.

77
00:11:44.360 --> 00:11:46.988
Ever consider having children?

78
00:11:48.697 --> 00:11:51.598
We just can't. I don't know
if it's his problem or mine.


79
00:11:51.700 --> 00:11:55.227
Don't worry!
You'll soon regain your youth,


80
00:11:56.271 --> 00:11:58.899
as well as the heart of your man.

81
00:12:12.221 --> 00:12:15.122
Do you have more potent stuff
for faster results?


82
00:12:16.825 --> 00:12:20.261
The best are those
in the fifth or sixth month.


83
00:12:20.362 --> 00:12:24.264
You have to remove it only by breaking
the water sac, then sliding it out.


84
00:12:24.366 --> 00:12:27.460
It's covered by a layer of creamy fat.

85
00:12:27.569 --> 00:12:31.027
The colors are defined.
You can even see the cranium.


86
00:12:32.474 --> 00:12:35.034
Its tiny limbs will
still be moving around.


87
00:12:37.146 --> 00:12:39.774
It's only this big
in the first trimester.


88
00:12:39.882 --> 00:12:44.046
But the meat will be tough
by the third trimester.


89
00:12:44.153 --> 00:12:47.554
The fifth-month ones
are perfect, kitten-like.


90
00:12:47.656 --> 00:12:50.124
So cute and so nutritious.

91
00:12:50.826 --> 00:12:52.589
Let me show you.

92
00:13:23.592 --> 00:13:26.152
I'm serving it pan-fried this time.

93
00:13:26.261 --> 00:13:29.662
We can always try some
other styles next time.


94
00:13:33.435 --> 00:13:36.632
