103
00:14:25.287 --> 00:14:27.255
No! It's much better!

104
00:14:27.356 --> 00:14:30.189
I need your most potent stuff.

105
00:14:30.292 --> 00:14:32.487
Trust me, I'll find it.

106
00:14:32.594 --> 00:14:34.459
It's time for me to sing.

107
00:14:35.497 --> 00:14:39.297
- Suit yourself, but I must go.
- Bye, Mrs. Li.


108
00:14:40.602 --> 00:14:42.069
This way!

109
00:14:43.171 --> 00:14:46.629
- Don't worry, I'll find it for you.
- Call me when you do.


110
00:14:46.742 --> 00:14:48.733
Trust me.

111
00:14:51.113 --> 00:14:52.978
Aunt Mei?

112
00:14:53.081 --> 00:14:55.572
