137
00:16:36.752 --> 00:16:38.549
Stay calm! And on my count...

138
00:16:38.654 --> 00:16:41.020
One, two, three!

139
00:16:43.158 --> 00:16:44.682
Where are my tongs?

140
00:16:45.594 --> 00:16:47.084
Relax!

141
00:16:58.807 --> 00:17:00.798
Try to relax.

142
00:17:08.517 --> 00:17:10.417
Beautiful.

143
