154
00:20:31.052 --> 00:20:32.986
It's a first-born,
the most nutritious.


155
00:20:33.088 --> 00:20:35.420
Nothing in the world
can beat this nutrition.


156
00:20:35.523 --> 00:20:41.462
The mother's a schoolgirl...
young and healthy.


157
00:20:41.563 --> 00:20:43.190
Then get working!

158
00:20:44.232 --> 00:20:45.426
What's the style today?

159
00:21:59.874 --> 00:22:04.436
This will make you
feel like new, I promise.


160
00:22:24.165 --> 00:22:25.359
