178
00:27:30.538 --> 00:27:33.200
Kate? Are you all right?

179
00:27:33.308 --> 00:27:35.799
Kate, what's going on?

180
00:27:35.910 --> 00:27:39.710
Answer me, Kate! Answer me!

181
00:27:39.814 --> 00:27:43.910
Kate? You all right?
