232
00:31:45.226 --> 00:31:47.922
- You sure there's no mistake?
- Not a chance.


233
00:31:48.029 --> 00:31:52.523
This is the best news
for both Mr. Li and you!


234
00:31:52.633 --> 00:31:55.329
